fixHouse:
    play sound click
    choice:
        "Your cottage is a picturesque place, save for the massive hole in the roof. Fortunately you now possess the tools required to fix it."
        "[Repair your roof] <span class='prompt'>[[-1 ACTION]]</span>" if (>= $stats.actions.value 1):
            play sound spendAction
            play sound spendAction
            set data.game_map.inHouse false
            add_stat actions -1
            run transition_black intro_hole
            clear_dialog
        "<span class='prompt'>[[BACK]]</span>":
            jump home

    "The hole left behind by Orb still haunts your nights. Leering over you like a sleep paralysis demon."
    "Your neighbours assume an old timey cannonball fired during the Frankish war of the Red Maple just took a long time to come back down and somehow found its way into your bedroom."
    if (!= $stats.day.value 1):
        "The floorboards beneath the hole are damp. It rained in the night."
    "It's a good job you're fixing this now, or you might have caught your death of cold."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        talk orb talk "We have everything we need to get this fixed up. We're all set."
        "Okay. Good. How do I fix things?":
            talk lovely talk "Goodness if I know, darling. I usually get the stable girl to do my repairs. She always looks ever so gallant... muscles gleaming with sweat... breathing heavy from exertion..."
            talk lovely talk "Oh me oh my... one must admit that often one creates little messes on purpose, solely to see her work... a broken bannister here, a list bit of arson there..."
            clear_dialog
            talk nasty talk "Right. Shut the fuck up Lovely Lady. Shut the fuck Orb. Shut up Lovely Lady. The big girls are talking."
            talk lovely talk "Gasp! How rude!"
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk nasty talk "Ghost, let's get too it cunt. Roll up your sleeves, hold the plank over the hole, and whack in some fucking nails. Simple as."
                "Simple as. [Do up the house]":
                    clear_dialog
                    play sound hammer
                    wait 6000
                    run transition intro_home
                    set data.ghost.roofRepaired true
                    remove_item planks 1
                    remove_item nails 1
                    complete_objective fixHouse fixHouse
                    if (objective_started? fixHouse fixHouseUrgent):
                        complete_objective fixHouse fixHouseUrgent
                    complete_quest fixHouse fixHouseSuccess
    "It takes a while."
    clear_dialog
    "Actually, it takes more than a while. You're clumsy and weak. You drop the plank on your foot."
    "Twice."
    clear_dialog
    "And the hammer on your toes."
    "Thrice."
    clear_dialog
    choice:
        "You huff and growl, but eventually your cottage once more has a roof (mostly)."
        "[Pat yourself on the back] \\"Good job, Ghost, you did it.\\"":
            "You pat yourself on the back with your hammer. It hurts a little."
            clear_dialog
            choice:
                talk nasty talk "Bopper job. You don't fancy getting into doing up the house full time do you eh? Lots of dosh in it..."
                "Maybe! I did find it a lot of fun! I liked hitting the nails! [Get really serious and somber] I did not like when I hit my fingie.":
                    talk nasty talk "Bopper."
                "I think doing up the house is too much work for me. I'm so so small and weak and pathetic.":
                    talk nasty talk "Eh, that's okay. Leaves more chicks for me to impress."
    clear_dialog
    talk orb talk "You did a good job, Ghost."
    choice:
        talk lovely talk "And it will be rather nice not to have rainwater making its way into your bedroom, don't you think?"
        "Agreed.":
            talk lovely talk "Wheee! Oh darling, I do love it when people agree with me!"
        "[Shake your head] I'm a fool... my source of drinking water... gone...":
            talk orb talk "Worry not, Ghost. They've invented 'taps'."
    clear_dialog
    talk nasty talk "Bloody hel. I'm genuinely fucking proud of you Ghost."
    choice:
        talk nasty talk "Love to see a dainty little homo like you learn to use a hammer. I'd shed a tear if I hadn't got glue in my eye earlier. I've been sniffing glue this whole time, by the way."
        "We all deserve some glue on this blessed day. <span class='prompt'>[[CONTINUE]]</span>":
            play sound spendAction
            jump goToGameMap